with the organisation I am hooked into. As you might have noticed Activa is
present as an account on my system, they do not have a usenet connection 
themselves. This is quite expensive in the netherlands (500-600 UKPounds a year
just for the fees).

So we are trying to get something together, but it might take a while.

 > > The BBS and registration of your software is the only way to obtain updates
