 > the areas via internet (like any "professional" comms setup)? 

nowhere is said you have a right to internet access by owning a registered
piece of software. Support is handled through the BBS and the fact activa 
is present on usenet is an added bonus. Don't think the whole world is on
usenet, this is just a SMALL percentage.

