From john@heights.demon.co.uk Sun May 23 18:29:20 1993
Date: Sun, 23 May 93 18:29:20 GMT
Reply-To: john@heights.demon.co.uk
From: John Shiali <john@heights.demon.co.uk>
Subject: YET another bug?

Is it just me? The tutorial on making the table on page 1.9 (ish) if
