RS-170A spec with it`s output signal.  On scopes, it's output is well within
the range considered good enough for broadcast.  I have not seen such claims
or figures from OpalVision _yet_.
Also, many...MANY production houses I have been to and atleast one station I
have been to work with composite signals and not component.

