 CP> purported to be a "professional" or at least professionally produced,
 CP> package ready for use 

More back pedalling. They could have told us before that they did not
consider us to be professional or deserving of professional software.
Now, I`m sure they will do what they can do make it much better, and
I`m glad, I just wish this had never happened.


 CP> Real 1.4 pro turbo was a professional package, aimed at
 CP> professionals. I don't think it was unreasonable of me to expect the
