Rousseau (R3D beta tester) which includes a reasonably complex test scene with
image texture maps. You may redesign the test object using other primitives,
I only ask that you post your results with the polygonal render times as well
since that is an apples to apples comparison and the only one I am truly
interested in. Since this represents a very small piece of some of my work
in progress, I thought it would be fairly representative of a real world
situation.

